Text: 'We decide to go to journey to tourism in forest we arrive to strange place
  full of big trees

  We made food and start to play acard game and other group go to swim, for awhile
  we hear a shouting, my friend want to sank we pulled him out

  And other group found ahuge snake and the kill them

  I''m very scared what this bad place we came to it

  We make lunch, meat and breads and drink atea and coffee

  The driver go and been drunk

  When we want go back he wached his face to drive a car but he still can''t see alot

  Some my friend with him to tell him the rood

  We start to go back

  The driver drive in no strat way

  I feel that we will die now

  Cilent cover all of us and driver go out to road and come back again and he is too
  fast. After a while the car is stoped and more moving

  Me and tow friend go and ride another car and went backe to city'
